<author>ḥnạ, rymwn mdḥt</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- sạ̉dkẖl byt ạlqdyr ḥytẖ ạlsʿạdh wạlsrwr sạ̉ḥtmy̱ fy̱ ḥḍnh ṭwl ạlmdy̱ ʿbr ạldhwr
 sạ̉ḥyạ dwmạ fy̱ ḥmạh ḥytẖ ạlḥyạh dwn ạnthạʾ
 sạ̉nsy̱ kl mạ mḍy̱ fy̱ ʿạlm ạlḍyq wạlạnyn
 symsḥ dmʿ ạlʿywn wybhj ạlqlb ạlḥzyn
 ạlqrạr - stkẖtfy̱ kl ạlhmwm kl ạlḍyqạt wạlạlạm
 syrfʿ kl ạljrạḥ ymlạ̉ fw̉ạdy̱ bạlslạm
 2- sạ̉rtwy̱ mn ḥbh sạ̉rtwy̱ ṭwl ạlzmạn
 sạ̉skn fy̱ qrbh ḥytẖ ạlskynh wạlạmạn
 sạ̉bqy̱ fy̱ ḥmy̱ ạby̱ ʿly̱ ạldwạm ṭwl ạlḥyạh
 sybqy̱ dwmạ qạỷdy̱ nbʿ kẖlạṣy̱ wạlrjạʾ</lyrics>
<title>sạ̉dkẖl byt ạlqdyr</title>
</song>